3824\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1315:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/wordpress-instagram-plugin.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" title=\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\" alt=\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">Instagram is a cool, informal picture-sharing platform and has taken the world by storm in a short while. The social media got deserved attention and exposure for all the right reasons. Today, most businesses have an Instagram page for their company to reach out to a wide audience. The platform boasts of more than 400 [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Walter Moore\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4684:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/wordpress-instagram-plugin.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" title=\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\" alt=\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Instagram is a cool, informal picture-sharing platform and has taken the world by storm in a short while. The social media got deserved attention and exposure for all the right reasons. Today, most businesses have an Instagram page for their company to reach out to a wide audience. The platform boasts of more than 400 million users. And it is no wonder why the top brands are latching on to this photo-sharing site for the success of their business. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many companies today use the Instagram\nStories feature to make their business presence felt. Then, why should web\ndesign be an exception? According to an article published on <a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/322742\">https://www.entrepreneur.com</a>, your business should be a part of\nInstagram for numerous reasons. One is 20 percent of stories posted by brands,\nleveraging the platform, lead to direct interaction with a prospective\ncustomer. Therefore, read on to learn about some of the tips to include\nInstagram in web design via WordPress. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Embed\nfeeds </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to incorporate Instagram into\nyour website design is by embedding the feeds. You may have an Instagram theme\nthat would gel well with your website colors, graphics, logos, and existing\nproducts. Make the most out of the platform to make the integration unified. You\ncan embed your Instagram content through a plug-in. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to experts in the industry, a\nplug-in comes with enhanced functionalities. Let us explain this point with the\nhelp of an example. You can add your images to the website gallery and\nintegrate a slider. The plug-in will let you backup your Instagram images and\nvideos to your website. Additionally, you can display these together with\ncustomized taxonomies. Moreover, when the users like your photos and videos, it\nwill help you gain more <a href=\"https://instamacro.com/\">Instagram\nfollowers</a>\nin the process. Besides, you can gain control of imported posts that will\nundergo formatting for getting custom post types and post formats. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Include\nInstagram badge </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Opt for the integrations that work best\nfor your web design. If your website has a flawless design with flying graphics\nor animations, for example, there is nothing like it. The inclusion of the Instagram\nlogo with other social media logos at the bottom of the left-hand corner of your\nsite is extremely important. The dark base highlights the white color without\ndistracting users from your website’s unique design and high-resolution images.\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Include\na page with sales in focus</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can design a web page with sales in\nfocus. When companies such as White Fox Boutique can create a page with sales\nintent, why not you? Moreover, Instagram has started to include e-businesses\ninto it via its latest initiative Instagram for business. Then, advertising\ncosts are very high and can go up to $350,000 to $1 million per month. If you\nhave supernormal profits, you can afford such expenses. On the contrary, if you\nown a startup or small business, such advertising expenses are not within your\nmeans. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make the most out of Instagram to\nintegrate into your web design. Therefore, as a designer, look for innovative\nways to enhance your web pages design and its reach to the global audience. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Author Bio:</strong> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Walter Moore is a notable management consultant and digital\nmarketing expert. He has helped e-commerce businesses in all niches gain <a href=\"https://instamacro.com/\">Instagram\nfollowers</a> with his effective marketing\nstrategies and guidance.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"Factors To Consider For Creating A Better Instagram Marketing Strategy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:105:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 16 Mar 2019 10:10:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Social Media\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://oceanwp.org/?p=389146\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1322:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-248533.jpeg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"Factors To Consider For Creating A Better Instagram Marketing Strategy\" alt=\"Factors To Consider For Creating A Better Instagram Marketing Strategy\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">You may have come across people talking about Instagram marketing strategy but may not know how to go about it. Well, it needs a little effort and a strategic approach considering the different factors involved in it. If you give a little of your time you will be able to make the most of the [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Walter Moore\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8064:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-248533.jpeg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"Factors To Consider For Creating A Better Instagram Marketing Strategy\" alt=\"Factors To Consider For Creating A Better Instagram Marketing Strategy\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>You may have come across people\ntalking about Instagram marketing strategy but may not know how to go about it.\nWell, it needs a little effort and a strategic approach considering the\ndifferent factors involved in it. If you give a little of your time you will be\nable to make the most of the 800 million active monthly users of this platform\nthat has more than 8 million business accounts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a mobile-based photo\nvideo-sharing social network platform that will allow you to reach to your targeted\ndemographics to engage them in a better way to drive more real social value as\nwell. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to studies, nearly\n60% of the <a href=\"https://gramista.com/\">Instagram followers</a> are young between the age group of 18 to 29 years. Therefore,\nInstagram is a highly competitive network through which you can reach out to this\nvaluable demographic. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Joining Instagram with their\ndigital marketing strategy, brands get a unique and enhanced opportunity to engage\nwith their fans in a better way. However, success for brands on Instagram needs\nmuch more than posting attractive images. You will need a:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Thoughtful strategy</li><li>Well-defined brand identity</li><li>Grounded visual creativity and </li><li>Effective community management. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You must also have a clear goal\nto achieve measurable results and follow a strategic and comprehensive guide.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You must focus on specific\nfeatures while <a href=\"https://www.quicksprout.com/2018/06/25/how-to-drive-sales-with-your-instagram-marketing-strategy/\">building\nyour Instagram marketing strategy</a> that includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Social media engagement </li><li>Instagram management</li><li>Instagram analytics</li><li>Audience targeting</li><li>Publishing calendar and</li><li>The objectives.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from these, you must also\nlook out for the best answers to a few specific questions such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>What do you want to achieve through Instagram? </li><li>What is the purpose of your brand for using\nInstagram? </li><li>What will Instagram allow you to do that the other\nplatforms will not?</li><li>Who is your target audience?</li><li>Which are the members of your audience that are most\nactive on Instagram?</li><li>How will Instagram integrate with the other social\nmedia networks in your marketing strategy?</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>It is only when you have your\nfocus and your objectives aligned, you will be able to showcase your culture, people,\nproducts and services through this unique platform.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Provides\nyou a better opportunity</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you use the mobile nature of\nInstagram perfectly for showing captured or in-the-moment pictures, you will\nget a better opportunity to give your Instagram followers a more personal scope\nto interact with your brand. It will also help you to engage in a way in which\nthe users will feel more casual, comfortable and instantaneous as compared with\nany other social media network.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on the type of\nbusiness you are involved with and the industry, you will have to consider the key\nperformance indicators according to your brand to make sure that your Instagram\nmarketing strategy is able to target your specific objectives that may include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Increasing brand awareness</li><li>Demonstrating company culture</li><li>Showcasing your team </li><li>Recruiting new talent</li><li>Increasing customer loyalty and engagement</li><li>Showcasing your products and services</li><li>Enhancing and complementing event experiences</li><li>Incentivizing consumer engagement</li><li>Sharing industry and company news</li><li>Building a more engaging community</li><li>Connecting with the influencers and </li><li>Driving sales through more organic traffic.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>When you create your Instagram\nmarketing strategy, these are the specific objectives that will guide you through\nthe process and help you to determine the best approach in each phase of the\nentire process. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Following\nthe best content strategy</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The primary requirement to make\nyour Instagram marketing strategy success is to develop ana better content strategy\nas this is the foundation of the entire process. A clearly defined and easy to\nunderstand content will determine your Instagram presence. There are several B2C\nbusinesses that use Instagram to make their product stand out and there are\nseveral other B2B companies on the other hand that often focus on team\nrecruitment and company culture. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, the best approach is to\nshow caseyour brand and develop a plan that is based on the objectives and\nneeds of the target audience. This will help you to deliver eye-catching\ncontent on a consistent basis to your community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also have to follow a\nfew other steps to build a better and produce a highly effective Instagram\ncontent. One such is building proper <a href=\"http://chroniclerepublic.com/8-instagram-content-themes-to-boost-engagement/\">Instagram\ncontent themes</a>. For this, you will have to make sure that you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Review your objectives</li><li>Determine the different aspects of your brand</li><li>Showcase the best content or pictures in your\nInstagram account</li><li>Consider posting pictures of your products,\nservices, company culture and your team members with proper balance</li><li>Offer rich potential for the subject matter over\ntime. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have a clear\nobjective, you must make a list of the specific content themes. You must then brainstorm\nall the possible subjects of your images and videos and make sure that you\nselect the ones that are perfectly suitable and relevant to your product or\nservices. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, you must ensure that\nyour content themes align with your brand voice and are visually appealing as\nwell. For example, you can use similar visuals that will help you tell a better\nstory but make sure that these pictures are vibrant and colorful. The content must\nhighlight the product in such a way that it increases interaction through clicks\nand traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>To\nsum it up</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lots of studies and surveys\nhave found out that Instagram photos and videos with faces are very useful to generate\nlikes and comments. In fact, these pictures generate 38% more likes in\ncomparison to those that do not have any faces. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to build a proper\nand more effective Instagram marketing strategy you must make sure that you\nbuild your content themes considering what you know works well. The best way to\nensure this is by using the Instagram analytics tool. This will help you to benchmark\nyour content and at the same time, it will help you to see what the things are that\nactually drive engagement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do not start your market strategy building process without having the proper data. Always conduct a quick Instagram audit so that you will know about all those things that you need to know.<font color=\"#191e23\"><span><b> </b></span></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:101:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/factors-to-consider-for-creating-a-better-instagram-marketing-strategy/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				