s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24469:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for your restaurant website? A restaurant website usually includes a menu, images, and other important features to entice hungry customers. However, creating a professional website for your restaurant all starts with selecting an attractive, functional theme.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 20 best WordPress restaurant themes currently on the market.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-foodica/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Foodica\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Foodica</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-foodica/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Foodica\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica.jpg\" alt=\"Foodica\" width=\"775\" height=\"339\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230354\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica-300x131.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica-768x336.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Foodica is a WordPress theme for restaurants, recipe websites, food bloggers, and magazines. It has multiple color schemes, a recipe index to post tempting recipes, and ad space to earn money from your website. Foodica supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, and it has an image slider to display mouthwatering food photos.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-belise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Belise\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Belise</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-belise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Belise\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise.jpg\" alt=\"Belise\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230355\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Belise is a multipurpose WordPress restaurant theme. It comes with a 1-click demo installer to launch your restaurant website. Belise is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/seo-friendly/\" title=\"How to Make Your WordPress Site SEO Friendly\">optimized for SEO</a> and speed. It comes with custom backgrounds, mega menus, and a powerful live customizer. It has WooCommerce integration to sell food online. The theme is translation-ready so you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Coffee\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Hestia Coffee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Coffee\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee.jpg\" alt=\"Hestia coffee\" width=\"775\" height=\"339\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230356\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee-300x131.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee-768x336.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hestia Coffee is a template used by the Hestia Pro theme for WordPress. It&#8217;s a perfect theme for your restaurant website. With all the features of Hestia Pro, you can create a multipurpose site or coffee blog easily. It has parallax scrolling, elegant homepage sections, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce</a> support, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-downtown/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Downtown\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Downtown</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-downtown/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Downtown\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown.jpg\" alt=\"Downtown\" width=\"1239\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230357\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown.jpg 1239w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown-768x356.jpg 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown-1024x475.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1239px) 100vw, 1239px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Downtown is a WordPress restaurant theme built specifically to create beautiful restaurant websites, food blogs, and online recipe magazines. It&#8217;s a smart choice for chefs to share their recipes in a professional, modern style. It has a custom logo, social share icons, widgets, and Google Maps to display your location. Downtown has a stunning <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Slider Plugins (Compared)\">homepage slider</a> to display your food photos.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurant-and-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurant and Cafe\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Restaurant and Cafe</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurant-and-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurant and Cafe\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe.jpg\" alt=\"Restaurant and Cafe\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230359\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re just starting your restaurant business and looking for an affordable WordPress theme, then go for Restaurant and Cafe. It&#8217;s a free WordPress restaurant theme with basic features to create a beautiful food or bakery website. It comes with a restaurant menu section, testimonials section, an online reservation system, and an image slider. You can use this theme to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online food store</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Ambiance Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro.jpg\" alt=\"Ambiance Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230360\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ambiance Pro is a modern WordPress theme for restaurant websites. It&#8217;s built on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"nofollow\">Genesis theme framework</a> which makes it a powerful theme. It allows you to display images and featured posts on the homepage. Ambiance Pro has a customizable header, widgets, theme options, and page templates.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-delicio/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Delicio\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Delicio</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-delicio/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Delicio\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio.jpg\" alt=\"Delicio\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230361\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Delicio is a stylish WordPress theme to create a restaurant, coffee shop, or bakery website. It has a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop page builder</a>, sliding sidebar, welcome message area, food menu, Google Maps support, and a responsive design. Delicio has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce support</a> to sell online. It has a team section to display photos of your restaurant&#8217;s staff and chefs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-carbone/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Carbone\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Carbone</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-carbone/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Carbone\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone.jpg\" alt=\"Carbone\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230362\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Carbone is an elegant WordPress restaurant and cafe theme. It features a menu management system, online reservation form, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">page builders</a> support, and a live theme customizer. Carbone is fully <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">optimized for SEO</a> and speed performance. It&#8217;s translation-ready and can be used to create a multilingual restaurant blog or website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurante/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurante\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Restaurante</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurante/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurante\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante.jpg\" alt=\"Restaurante\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230363\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Restaurante is a free WordPress theme for your restaurant, barbecue, grill house, fast food, pizzerias, or other food-related website. It has a customizable background, header, and menu. Restaurante supports open graph and Twitter cards to gain popularity on social media channels. It has both multi-column and full-width templates.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cafe Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Cafe Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cafe Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro.jpg\" alt=\"Cafe Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230364\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Cafe Pro is a WordPress <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"nofollow\">Genesis</a> theme. It can be used to create a beautiful and modern cafe website. The theme is perfect for a full-fledged restaurant or food blog. It has a parallax design, homepage widgets, menu system, online reservation, location support, and more. Cafe Pro comes with custom page templates and theme options to design your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert\">landing pages</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-igloo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Igloo\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Igloo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-igloo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Igloo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo.jpg\" alt=\"Igloo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230365\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Igloo is a unique and powerful WordPress restaurant theme. It allows you to post your food photos professionally via a built-in <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">image gallery</a>. It has an amazing menu management system to display starters, main courses, and desserts with their prices. Igloo has multiple color schemes and 4 content types. It has custom widgets and is optimized for speed.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-seasons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Seasons\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Seasons</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-seasons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Seasons\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons.jpg\" alt=\"Seasons\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230366\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Seasons is a professional restaurant WordPress theme. It includes multiple layouts for a cafe, bar, restaurant, or other food-based websites. Like other restaurant themes, it has a food menu system and allows online reservations. It comes with a unique slideshow that can be used to display events, food photos, menus, and more. Seasons supports a blog template for food bloggers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-listee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Listee\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Listee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-listee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Listee\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee.jpg\" alt=\"Listee\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230367\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Listee is a business directory and listing theme for WordPress. If you want to create a list of local restaurants, then Listee is the perfect choice. It has a responsive layout, flexible search system, front-end list submissions, and a live theme customizer. It comes with a drag and drop page builder to create landing pages and business directories.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-petit/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Petit\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Petit</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-petit/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Petit\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit.jpg\" alt=\"Petit\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230368\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Petit is a food recipe theme for WordPress websites. On the homepage, there&#8217;s a featured area and carousel slider to post your recipes. It has a rating system to allow your users to rate the recipes and request more cuisines. Petit features custom widgets, recipe shortcodes, a theme options panel, and an Instagram widget. With the custom posts feature, you can easily separate a recipe post and display it on the homepage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-mise-en-place/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mise En Place\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Mise En Place</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-mise-en-place/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mise En Place\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace.jpg\" alt=\"Mise En Place\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230369\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Mise En Place is a WordPress theme for chefs and restaurants. It supports custom logos, Google Fonts, unlimited colors, and a live customizer to style your website. It has a page builder to drag and drop features and content. The menu can be added with thumbnails and you can display it in the sidebar using a widget. Mise En Place has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce integration</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/lzrestaurant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lzrestaurant\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Lzrestaurant</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/lzrestaurant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lzrestaurant\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant.jpg\" alt=\"Lzrestaurant\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230370\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Lzrestaurant is another free WordPress restaurant theme. It&#8217;s built for food critics and bloggers to write about cafes, restaurants, bars, and food businesses. It can also be used to sell food reviews. The testimonials section allows you to collect feedback from users on the critics. Lzrestaurant has social media integration, an SEO-friendly design, and a lightweight layout.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/quna/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quna\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Quna</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/quna/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quna\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna.jpg\" alt=\"Quna\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230371\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Quna is a minimal WordPress theme for restaurant and cafe websites. It has a post archive page to save your food blogs and recipes for users. It comes with social media support, and you can display food photos from your Instagram feed. It allows you to import the demo data and change the content to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-food-recipe-website/\" title=\"How to Create a Food &#038; Recipe Website (and Make Money)\">launch your restaurant website and make money</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-umami/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Umami\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Umami</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-umami/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Umami\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami.jpg\" alt=\"Umami\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230351\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Umami is a modern restaurant theme for WordPress. It has WooCommerce support to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online store</a> and sell your food products. It comes with a fullscreen background slideshow to display food photos. The navigation menu is in the sidebar with your restaurant&#8217;s hours of operation, address, and social icons. Umami has a powerful system to display your restaurant&#8217;s menu in your pages, widget areas, and posts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-moonrise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Moonrise\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Moonrise</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-moonrise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Moonrise\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise.jpg\" alt=\"Moonrise\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230352\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Moonrise is a WordPress theme for restaurants, cafes, bars, and taverns. It has multiple templates including a 1-page template, blog template, inner-pages templates, and more. Moonrise has a long homepage with up to 7 sections to display your food menu, services, slideshow, contact details, widgets, and content. It offers easy customization to add your logo, change fonts, create image galleries, and manage theme colors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-salt-pepper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Salt and Pepper\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Salt and Pepper</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-salt-pepper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Salt and Pepper\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper.jpg\" alt=\"Salt and Pepper\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230353\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Salt and Pepper is a WordPress recipe theme used to share tempting recipes and cooking tips with your users. It has all the standard website pages including about, contact, blog, and more. The theme comes with a drag and drop layout to easily add features and content on your website. It has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> support to create a translation-ready site or blog.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress restaurant themes. You may also want to check out our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/\" title=\"21 Best WordPress Real Estate Themes (Compared)\">best WordPress real estate themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/\">20 Best WordPress Restaurant Themes Compared (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\