32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=229826\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:627:\"<p>Do you want to create branded email accounts from your domain name? After purchasing your domain name, you&#8217;ll have the opportunity to get associated email accounts with it. Using an email address branded with your domain name is a great way to give off professional vibe to your potential customers. You can even create multiple [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\">How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22331:\"<p>Do you want to create branded email accounts from your domain name? After purchasing your domain name, you&#8217;ll have the opportunity to get associated email accounts with it. Using an email address branded with your domain name is a great way to give off professional vibe to your potential customers. You can even create multiple email accounts associated with your domain, so your team members can better represent your brand. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to properly create email accounts for your domain name and use them to send emails.</p>\n<h3>Why Should You Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name?</h3>\n<p>Most email addresses you&#8217;ll see end with gmail.com, live.com, aol.com, etc. These email addresses are great for personal use, but aren&#8217;t recommended for businesses, or anyone else looking to portray a professional image.</p>\n<p>First of all, if your name is relatively common, then you most likely won&#8217;t get your desired email address. You&#8217;ll end up adding numbers or additional letters to your email address (ex: dan.brown321@gmail.com) which doesn&#8217;t look professional. In fact, it looks downright spammy.</p>\n<p>If you have a business then you&#8217;ll need a simple email address that represents yourself and your company name.</p>\n<p>You can achieve that by creating email addresses for your domain name. Check out this example:</p>\n<p><strong>Your Domain Name:</strong></p>\n<p>www.example.com</p>\n<p><strong>Your Email Address:</strong></p>\n<p>dan.brown@example.com or dan@example.com</p>\n<p>From the above example, you can easily see the difference between a personal and a professional email address. Emails sent using your own domain name will quickly gain the trust of your users, and it&#8217;s a great way to conduct business-related communication.</p>\n<h3>Setting Up Email Accounts for Your Domain Name</h3>\n<p>To create business email accounts, you&#8217;ll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If you already have a domain name and web hosting, then skip to the next step.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 1. Register a Domain Name and Web Hosting</strong></p>\n<p>You can check out the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/choose-best-domain-name-registrar/\" title=\"How to Choose the Best Domain Name Registrar\">top domain name registrars</a> to purchase your professional business name online. Not only can you buy a domain name, but these registrars will also suggest other business name options.</p>\n<p>After getting your domain name, you&#8217;ll need to connect it with a web hosting account. You&#8217;ll need to do this before you can create email accounts for your domain name.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> for web hosting. It&#8217;s the most popular hosting company in the world.</p>\n<p>For IsItWP users, they&#8217;re offering a free domain name, a free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png\" alt=\"bluehost-register-domain-name-free\" width=\"740\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228494\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Once you have your domain name and web hosting, you&#8217;ll need to log into your Bluehost account to create your email accounts.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2. Log Into Your Hosting cPanel and Create Your Email Accounts</strong></p>\n<p>First, you&#8217;ll need to log into your cPanel account. If you&#8217;re using Bluehost, then the cPanel will look like this:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel.jpg\" alt=\"Bluehost cPanel\" width=\"774\" height=\"346\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230792\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel-300x134.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel-768x343.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to click the &#8216;Email and Office&#8217; tab from the left-hand navigation menu and click on the &#8216;Manage&#8217; button to get started.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails.jpg\" alt=\"Manage emails\" width=\"775\" height=\"334\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230793\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails-768x331.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>On the next page, you&#8217;ll find multiple tabs. Under the &#8216;Add Email Account&#8217; tab, you can enter your desired account name. Try something like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>dan@example.com</li>\n<li>info@example.com</li>\n<li>hello@example.com</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In the above example, &#8216;dan,&#8217; &#8216;info,&#8217; and &#8216;hello&#8217; are the usernames and &#8216;example.com&#8217; is your business/domain name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts.jpg\" alt=\"Create email accounts\" width=\"775\" height=\"395\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230794\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts-768x391.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Make sure that you don&#8217;t enter your domain name in this field as it&#8217;s already there. You don&#8217;t want to end up as &#8216;dan@example.com@example.com!&#8217;</p>\n<p>After choosing your account name, you can enter a secure password. If you can&#8217;t think of a secure enough password, Bluehost will offer to generate a random password for you which you can save before continuing.</p>\n<p>Next, you can add the Mailbox Quota. This quota depends on your hosting plan and we recommend you leave it as-is. By default, it&#8217;s set to 500 MB, which is a decent amount of space for an email account. You should have more than enough space; however, you can always increase or decrease it later, if needed.</p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Create Account&#8217; button to complete the process. You can make multiple email accounts for your domain name by repeating the above steps.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;re done, simply go to the &#8216;Email Accounts&#8217; tab to view all of the email addresses you created.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts.jpg\" alt=\"Email accounts\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230795\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts-300x118.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts-768x303.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Step 3. Access Your Email Account</strong></p>\n<p>To access your email accounts, you can click on the &#8216;Access Webmail&#8217; link next to an email address. It&#8217;ll open up an email client where you can see your new emails. You can also send emails from there.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail.jpg\" alt=\"Access webmail\" width=\"775\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230796\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail-300x147.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail-768x377.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to set up your email account on other devices, like your mobile phone, then click on the &#8216;Connect Devices&#8217; link; and then click on the &#8216;Set Up Mail Client&#8217; option.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;ll display the information you need to configure your email account on all major applications/devices. Luckily, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> offers automatic configurations to many apps and devices.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients.jpg\" alt=\"Set up email clients\" width=\"775\" height=\"450\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230797\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients-300x174.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients-768x446.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also find manual configuration options on that page for devices and applications that aren&#8217;t listed in the auto-config section.</p>\n<h3>Setting Up an Email Account with G Suite</h3>\n<p>Now that you have your email accounts, you can connect them with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gsuite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"G Suite\" rel=\"nofollow\">G Suite by Google Cloud</a> and use them from there. It&#8217;ll make your emailing experience a lot easier than using webmail by <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Why You Should Connect Your Email Account with G Suite</strong></p>\n<p>The email clients offered by Bluehost, or any other web hosting company, are not as simple or tidy as Gmail. Also, you won&#8217;t get additional apps like you will with G Suite. Webmail is a simple application to send and receive emails with no other features.</p>\n<p>However, you may use G Suite daily on your laptop and phone. G Suite includes all the popular Google apps like Gmail, Google Photos, Docs, Drive, etc.</p>\n<p>Once you connect your business email accounts with G Suite, you can access all their apps and features.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a premium service which means you&#8217;ll need to pay an additional cost other than the cost of a domain name and web hosting, but it&#8217;s well worth the price. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gsuite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"G Suite\" rel=\"nofollow\">G Suite</a> plans start from $5 per user / month. It&#8217;ll include resources separately for the number of accounts you purchase.</p>\n<p>First, you&#8217;ll need to go the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gsuite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"G Suite\" rel=\"nofollow\">G Suite</a> website and select a plan to get started.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan.jpg\" alt=\"Select a plan\" width=\"775\" height=\"368\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230828\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan-300x142.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan-768x365.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>On the next page, you&#8217;ll need to enter basic details about your business to continue.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite.jpg\" alt=\"Get started with G Suite\" width=\"775\" height=\"420\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230829\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite-300x163.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite-768x416.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, you&#8217;ll be asked if you have a domain name. Since you purchased your domain name in the previous section, you can select the option &#8216;I have a domain&#8217; and click on the &#8216;Next&#8217; button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain.jpg\" alt=\"Have a domain\" width=\"775\" height=\"395\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230830\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain-768x391.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, enter your business name or domain name and click the &#8216;Next&#8217; button again.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname.jpg\" alt=\"Enter domain name\" width=\"775\" height=\"292\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230831\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname-300x113.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname-768x289.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to add a username and password. This username will be the account name for your email and it&#8217;ll be attached to your domain name (dan@example.com).</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername.jpg\" alt=\"Enter username\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230832\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once signed up, you&#8217;ll see a success message showing that your account was created. This will be your primary email account (administrator account) for your domain name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated.jpg\" alt=\"G Suite account created\" width=\"775\" height=\"186\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230833\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated-300x72.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated-768x184.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Go to Setup&#8217; button to complete the account setup.</p>\n<p>On the setup screen, you should add your team members or other users to create more accounts. Simply check the &#8216;I added all user email addresses currently using [this domain]&#8217; option and click on the &#8216;Next&#8217; button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers.jpg\" alt=\"Add all users\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230834\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If you have a single email account, then you can skip this step.</p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to verify ownership for your domain name.</p>\n<p>Simply copy the meta tag, or upload an HTML file, to your hosting account for verification. Use only 1 method to verify domain ownership.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag.jpg\" alt=\"Meta tag\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230835\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to log into your website and install the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/insert-headers-and-footers/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Insert Headers and Footers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Insert Headers and Footers</a> plugin to do this. For more details, you can read our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"How to Install a WordPress Plugin\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Once the plugin&#8217;s activated, go to <strong>Settings &raquo; Insert Headers and Footer</strong> and enter the meta tag in the &#8216;Scripts in Header&#8217; text area.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader.jpg\" alt=\"Scripts in header\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230836\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Save&#8217; button and go back to your G Suite page to check &#8216;I added the meta tag to my homepage&#8217; option.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail.jpg\" alt=\"Verify email account\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230837\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll also need to enter MX records for your domain name to make the G Suite functional for your email accounts.</p>\n<p>The process of adding the MX records is quite similar for any domain name registrar. Since we&#8217;re using Bluehost, we&#8217;ll walk you through adding the entries in your Bluehost account.</p>\n<p>Log into your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> hosting account and visit the &#8216;Domains&#8217; page from the left-hand navigation menu.</p>\n<p>From there, you&#8217;ll need to select your domain name and click on the &#8216;Manage DNS records&#8217; link on the right side.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns.jpg\" alt=\"Manage DNS\" width=\"775\" height=\"322\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230838\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns-300x125.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns-768x319.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Go back to G Suite&#8217;s website and check &#8216;I have opened the control panel for my domain&#8217; option. You&#8217;ll now see the MX record entries that you can copy from there.</p>\n<p>Now, you can come back to your Bluehost account and enter the MX records.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords.jpg\" alt=\"Enter MX records\" width=\"775\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230839\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords-300x101.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords-768x258.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Add Record&#8217; button to continue.</p>\n<p>After that, go to G Suite&#8217;s website and check &#8216;I created the new MX records&#8217; option. You&#8217;ll also need to delete any existing MX record entries pointing to your domain name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords.jpg\" alt=\"Created MX records\" width=\"775\" height=\"192\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230840\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords-300x74.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords-768x190.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once deleted, you&#8217;ll also need to save the MX records manually and check the &#8216;I saved the MX records&#8217; option.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount.jpg\" alt=\"Verify domain name\" width=\"775\" height=\"363\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230841\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount-300x141.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount-768x360.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Last, click on the &#8216;Verify Domain and Set Up Email&#8217; button to complete the process. For more specific details, you can follow our complete tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-professional-business-email-with-g-suite/\" title=\"How to Create a Professional Branded Business Email with G Suite\">how to create a business email with G Suite</a>.</p>\n<p>You can go ahead and log into your email account using Gmail or the G Suite website. As an administrator, you can also manage all additional email accounts for your domain name.</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you learn how to create email accounts for your domain name. You may also want to check out our article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-free-business-email/\" title=\"How to Create a Free Business Email in Less than 5 Minutes\">how to create a free business email in less than 5 minutes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\">How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"10 Best Business Phone Services and Systems (2019)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 29 Mar 2019 08:26:25 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"best business phone services\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"grasshopper\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"nextiva\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"phonecom\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"ringcentral\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"small business phone service\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=228255\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:629:\"<p>Do you want the best business phone service for your WordPress site? Many small businesses integrate an online phone system on their websites to instantly connect with their users. It&#8217;s an additional service to live chat, email support, and other solutions on the market. In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best business phone services you [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/\">10 Best Business Phone Services and Systems (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13969:\"<p>Do you want the best business phone service for your WordPress site? Many small businesses integrate an online phone system on their websites to instantly connect with their users. It&#8217;s an additional service to live chat, email support, and other solutions on the market.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best business phone services you can use on your WordPress website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nextiva\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Nextiva</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nextiva\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva.jpg\" alt=\"Nextiva\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228256\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Nextiva is one of the most popular business phone and call forwarding services for small businesses. It&#8217;s easy to use and offers amazing features. Nextiva is an affordable service, which means <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps (2019)\">small business websites</a> can easily benefit from it. It has a web-based panel to manage your calls, voicemails, and faxes.</p>\n<p>Nextiva has a VOIP service that enables you to do free domestic calling, call routing, transfer voicemails to emails, and more. Their VOIP service is advanced yet beginner-friendly and easy to use. Other than that, the primary perk of using Nextiva is that it&#8217;ll provide you with a registered toll-free number which means your users can connect with you for free. It also offers other services like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Live Chat Software Plugins Compared (2019)\">live chat</a>, call analytics, CRM, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $19.95 / month with no setup fees.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Phone.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Phone.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Phone.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom.jpg\" alt=\"Phone.com\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228258\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Phone.com is the best business phone service for small businesses. It comes with a call routing service, call forwarding, fax, caller ID, multi-line (conference) calling, and more. Phone.com has both app-based and web-based panels to manage calls online.</p>\n<p>They have a cheap business phone line for many European countries and Canada which lets their users expand their businesses to those countries. Phone.com offer integration with many CRM software on the market including Zoho and Salesforce.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It comes with pay-per-minute and unlimited pricing plans. Starting from $9.99 / month if paid annually.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"RingCentral\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. RingCentral</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"RingCentral\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral.jpg\" alt=\"RingCentral\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228259\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>RingCentral is a hassle-free business phone service that can be used by small-to-large scale businesses easily. Like all other top business phone services, RingCentral comes with a call waiting option, call transfers, a multi-line phone system, call forwarding, conference calls, video conferencing, and more.</p>\n<p>It enables you to share screens, make free calls with their toll-free option, and works great with third-party services like Microsoft, Gusto, Dropbox, etc. RingCentral has a simple portal to launch business phone services and manage calls from users.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $19.99 / month. RingCentral also offers other custom plans to fulfill your needs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/8x8-phone-service/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"8x8\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. 8&#215;8</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/8x8-phone-service/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"8x8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service.jpg\" alt=\"8x8 Business phone service\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228262\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>8&#215;8 is a popular business phone service on the market. It&#8217;s a perfect fit for beginners who&#8217;re starting to add an internet business phone system on their websites. 8&#215;8 has fewer features than an average online phone solution, but it&#8217;s useful for small business owners.</p>\n<p>Their services include voicemail, automatic call answering, text, number sharing, and more. They offer several plans for their users to provide ease and reliability.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $24.99 / mo for each user (Also, 250 outbound minutes to the US and Canada)</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GrassHopper\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. GrassHopper</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GrassHopper\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper.jpg\" alt=\"GrassHopper\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228264\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>GrassHopper is the best virtual phone system for small business owners. It comes with all the standard VOIP service features like call forwarding, voicemail, caller ID, etc. It enables you to make calls using a regular phone number. Their extensions can be used to make conference calls, which is great for inbound team meetings.</p>\n<p>The web and app-based portal is easy to use. It comes with toll-free numbers for the US, UK, and Canada. GrassHopper has multiple extensions for phone numbers, toll-free numbers, and vanity numbers to make calls online.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $29.99 / month (1 number and up to 3 extensions)</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.vonage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vonage\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Vonage</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.vonage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vonage\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage.jpg\" alt=\"Vonage\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228268\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Vonage is another small business phone service that can be used for online calling. It comes with all the standard VOIP services, plus Amazon Chime, video calls, and more. Their premium services have more features and additional advanced technology for their users.</p>\n<p>Their web-based administration panel helps regulate calls, create users, and manage online communication in a smart way.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $19.99 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.skype.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Skype\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Skype</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skype.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Skype\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype.jpg\" alt=\"Skype\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228269\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Skype is the most popular phone system to make voice calls and conduct video conferences in the world. It offers unlimited free calls to other Skype users via an internet connection. However, when you want to make calls to international or local numbers, then you&#8217;ll need their premium credits.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s powered by Microsoft, which means the service has a solid foundation. You can also get a local number which users can call to connect with you on Skype.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Basic version is free to download. Enterprise plan starting from $8.25 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://voice.google.com/u/0/about\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Google Voice\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Google Voice</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://voice.google.com/u/0/about\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Google Voice\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice.jpg\" alt=\"Google Voice\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228274\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Google Voice is a flexible business phone service. However, it has fewer options when compared to a fully virtual phone system. It&#8217;s handy for smart phone users and business owners using devices that support Google products.</p>\n<p>It has a free US-based number, voicemail service, call recording, and more. Google Voice helps create better communication between business owners and consumers.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> A free number to make calls, texts, and voicemails.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.voiceshot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Voiceshot\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Voiceshot</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.voiceshot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Voiceshot\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot.jpg\" alt=\"Voiceshot\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228271\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Voiceshot is an excellent business phone service for small websites. It comes with an auto respondent system to answer calls anytime which means you&#8217;re active even after business hours. Voiceshot allows you to send outbound messages to your users. You can also create custom, interactive outbound texts.</p>\n<p>It helps with call scheduling and sends alerts / reminders to you and your users about the call. Other features include emergency call alerts, integrations, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $12 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://callhippo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CallHippo\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. CallHippo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://callhippo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CallHippo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo.jpg\" alt=\"CallHippo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228273\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>CallHippo is one of the most popular virtual phone systems in the world. It has standard VOIP features like a phone number, caller ID, call forwarding, etc. You don&#8217;t need a desk phone to make calls using CallHippo as everything is managed from their online portal.</p>\n<p>It has a simple web-based portal to create users, manage calls, and more. You can also create departments and transfer calls to specific experts.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Basic set up is free for up to 2 users. Premium plans starting form $8 / month.</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you discover the best business phone services. If you liked this article, then you should also check out our guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-help-desk-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Help Desk Plugins for Customer Support\">9 best WordPress help desk plugins for customer support</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/\">10 Best Business Phone Services and Systems (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"9 Best Wix Alternatives to Easily Build a Site (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 12:27:03 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"weebly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"wix\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wix alternatives\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"wix competitors\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=229482\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:607:\"<p>Are you looking for popular alternatives to Wix? As one of the most popular website builders for beginners and startups, Wix is known for their easy-to-use drag and drop platform. Using Wix, you can create a basic website in mere minutes. However, if you want to expand your website, you&#8217;ll need to buy their expensive [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/\">9 Best Wix Alternatives to Easily Build a Site (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17639:\"<p>Are you looking for popular alternatives to Wix? As one of the most popular website builders for beginners and startups, Wix is known for their easy-to-use drag and drop platform. Using Wix, you can create a basic website in mere minutes. However, if you want to expand your website, you&#8217;ll need to buy their expensive premium extensions. As Wix becomes too costly, you may need to look for other website builders on the market.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 9 most popular Wix alternatives and competitors you can use.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. WordPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1.png\" alt=\"WordPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229506\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WordPress is a free content management system (CMS) and website builder. It&#8217;s used by over 32% of websites around the globe, which makes it the most-used platform in the world. Many <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">top brands use WordPress</a>  actively for their websites.</p>\n<p>By WordPress, we mean the self-hosted WordPress.org and not WordPress.com, a hosted solution. To avoid any confusion, we recommend you check out our in-depth article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a> for a full list of their differences.</p>\n<p>WordPress is a perfect alternative to Wix. Feel free to read our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wix-vs-wordpress/\" title=\"Wix vs. WordPress – Which One is the Best Choice? (Expert Review)\">Wix vs WordPress</a> for a complete side-by-side comparison. WordPress offers flexibility and customization that lacks in any other website builder. The themes and plugins in the WordPress repository help you design the website you need regardless of your skill level. Plus, you can find additional free and premium resources on the internet.</p>\n<p>Using WordPress will also give you a leg up on the competition if you need to build eCommerce sites. The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce plugin</a> for WordPress is free to use and it allows you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online store</a> with ease. With WooCommerce, you can use any other WordPress plugins to extend the functionality of your online business.</p>\n<p>The WordPress community is all over the world. If you have any trouble with your site, you can ask about your issue on the forums and social channels. We bet you&#8217;ll get the solution in no time. You should also check out IsItWP&#8217;s <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/snippets/\" title=\"Snippets\">Snippets</a> section for more customization options.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/weebly/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Weebly\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Weebly</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/weebly/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Weebly\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly.png\" alt=\"Weebly\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229901\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Weebly is a popular website builder. It has tons of designs to create a website instantly. It&#8217;s a fully hosted solution which means you can get started using their site right away. Weebly has a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop builder</a> to add text, images, and other content on your website.</p>\n<p>It also enables you to launch an online store and sell your products. Like your website, you won&#8217;t need external <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/free-web-hosting/\" title=\"Top 11 Best Free Web Hosting Companies (No B.S)\">web hosting</a> or bandwith for your eCommerce business. Everything is available on Weebly&#8217;s site, and you can start just by entering details about your store. They offer plenty of paid extensions to add more features to your website or online shop.</p>\n<p>Weebly has a strong support team to help resolve your issues. You can also use their community section to find a solution to any of your problems related to website making. Check out our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/weebly-review/\" title=\"Weebly Review – Is It the Best Choice for You?\">Weebly review</a> for more details.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Squarespace\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Squarespace</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Squarespace\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace.png\" alt=\"Squarespace\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229498\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Squarespace is a self-hosted website and eCommerce store builder. It has multiple web templates for photographers, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/\" title=\"How to Make an Online Portfolio on WordPress (Step by Step)\">online portfolio sites</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/\" title=\"20 Best WordPress Restaurant Themes Compared\">restaurants</a>, musicians, and more. These templates are highly professional and require little-to-no changes before you launch your website.</p>\n<p>It also comes with a powerful <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce solution</a>. You can create a fully functional online store with Squarespace in just a few clicks of your mouse. Their product pages can be customized to add images, descriptions, and other information. You can use their premium payment solutions for secure transactions.</p>\n<p>Squarespace email campaigns help grow your website traffic. You can use their powerful tools to extend your reach and get more online visitors. Also, check out these <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-alternatives-to-squarespace/\" title=\"11 Squarespace Alternatives for Every Kind of Website\">Squarespace alternatives</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BigCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. BigCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BigCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce.jpg\" alt=\"BigCommerce\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229503\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>BigCommerce is an eCommerce platform used to create online business stores. It allows you to list your products on Facebook, Amazon, and other top social / business networks to get more business. It&#8217;s a premium solution, but you can start with a free trial to test their software.</p>\n<p>It can easily compete with Wix&#8217;s eCommerce builder. BigCommerce has solutions for small businesses, B2B, enterprises, and big online shops. It offers premium tools to create a powerful store. The apps integration adds more features to your site, and you can also accept online payments without owing any fees to them.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shopify\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Shopify</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shopify\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1.png\" alt=\"Shopify\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229504\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Shopify is the most popular eCommerce platform on the market. It has a 14-day free trial to get to know the software and test everything before you setup your online store. You can use Shopify to sell online, on social media, on Amazon, or any other network. It&#8217;s a beginner-friendly solution with no coding skills required.</p>\n<p>If you plan to create an eCommerce shop with Wix, then you should also consider Shopify. With Shopify, you can manage unlimited products and inventory. It also allows you to track your orders and growth trends, so you&#8217;ll know your where you stand against your competitors.</p>\n<p>When it comes to website design, Shopify can be fully customized to change colors, fonts, backgrounds, and product page templates. You&#8217;ll be able to accept credit card payments, and it also integrates with other online payment solutions.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webnode/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Webnode\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Webnode</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webnode/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Webnode\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1.jpg\" alt=\"Webnode\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229500\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Webnode is an excellent website builder and an alternative to Wix. It comes with free and premium plans to create a website. The free plan has basic features and allows you to set up a site on the Webnode domain name. To <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-work/\" title=\"What is a Domain Name and How Does it Work? (Explained)\">register a custom domain name</a> and get other useful features, you&#8217;ll need their paid version.</p>\n<p>It has 50 web templates to design your site. These templates are free to use on Webnode. You can get started for free and upgrade to their premium plan when needed. The premium version has more to offer like a form builder, Google Analytics, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\" title=\"How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name\">email accounts</a>, etc.</p>\n<p>Webnode has their own <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/free-web-hosting/\" title=\"Top 11 Best Free Web Hosting Companies (No B.S)\">web hosting</a> that&#8217;s included with any premium plan. You can upgrade your plan for more hosting space. The free version has less space, but it&#8217;s enough for a small website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webstarts/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WebStarts\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. WebStarts</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webstarts/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WebStarts\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1.png\" alt=\"WebStarts\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229502\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WebStarts is a freemium website builder. It has both free and premium plans. You can get started with their free version and scale to a premium plan later if you need more advanced features. WebStarts comes with a drag and drop page builder to instantly launch your website. It&#8217;s a cheap solution that&#8217;s perfect for startups.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a hosted platform and needs no outside resources to build a website. The highlighted features include membership addons, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">SEO tools</a>, contact forms, and more. You can talk with their live support team to get answers to any questions regarding your WebStarts website.</p>\n<p>WebStarts can also be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a WordPress Blog (&#038; Make Extra Income)\">create a blog</a> or an online store. With all its features, you can use this platform to gain an online presence. It&#8217;s an alternative to Wix and other <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared\">popular website builders</a> with more app integrations.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mozello/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mozello\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Mozello</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mozello/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mozello\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1.png\" alt=\"Mozello\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229501\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Mozello is an excellent website building solution. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-register-a-domain-name/\" title=\"Beginner’s Guide: How to Register a Domain Name (+ Tip on How to Get It for FREE)\">register a free domain name</a>. You can create a website, blog, or an online store with Mozello. Their premium plans have tons of amazing <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\" title=\"15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress\">tools for marketing</a> and SEO. Plus, they include multilingual support so you can create a website in your native language.</p>\n<p>Like other website builders in this article, Mozello comes with a simple drag and drop module to quickly add elements and features onto your site. It has beautiful, professional designs to customize your website any way you want.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.jimdo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Jimdo\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Jimdo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jimdo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Jimdo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1.png\" alt=\"Jimdo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229499\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Jimdo is another website builder with powerful features to create a website. It&#8217;s based on artificial intelligence and understands users&#8217; requirements in a smart way. Jimdo offers a free domain name with their premium plans. Their excellent support team will help with all your website-related queries.</p>\n<p>This platform can also be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online store</a>. There&#8217;s no limit for adding products and no transaction fees. You can get the full profit of your sales when using Jimdo. It works great with popular payment solutions like PayPal and credit cards. You can also integrate SEPA Direct Card for online payments.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the most popular Wix alternatives and competitors. You may also want to check out our guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-alternatives-popular-wordpress-competitors/\" title=\"WordPress Alternatives – 18 Popular WordPress Competitors\">most popular WordPress alternatives</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/\">9 Best Wix Alternatives to Easily Build a Site (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"How to Pick the Best Domain Name (&amp; How to Get It for Free)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"https://www.isitwp.com/pick-best-domain-name/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/pick-best-domain-name/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 27 Mar 2019 15:52:30 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"choosing a domain name for a personal website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"domain name generator\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"domain name suggestions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"how to choose a domain name for your blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"how to pick the best domain name\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=228468\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:568:\"<p>Do you want to start a website but are struggling with how to pick the best domain name? A good domain name is important to the success of your website or blog. After all, it’s how your audience will find you on the world wide web. So, it can’t be just a split second decision; [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/pick-best-domain-name/\">How to Pick the Best Domain Name (&#038; How to Get It for Free)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13803:\"<p>Do you want to start a website but are struggling with how to pick the best domain name? A good domain name is important to the success of your website or blog. After all, it’s how your audience will find you on the world wide web. So, it can’t be just a split second decision; you’ve got to spend time to come up with the best domain name possible. Plus, there are some domain name best practices you should know about to help you pick the right domain name for your website. </p>\n<p>Luckily, in this article we’re going to share some tips and tricks for how to pick the best domain name. Once you find the perfect domain name for your website, we’ll then show you <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-register-a-domain-name/\">how to register your domain name for free</a>! Let’s begin. </p>\n<h3>1. Brainstorm Ideas and Research</h3>\n<p>The first step to picking the best domain name is to brainstorm some ideas and do some research. If you’re thinking about how to choose a domain name for your blog or website, then you’ve probably been thinking about <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\">starting a blog</a> or a business for awhile. So, you should have some ideas about what you want your blog to be about or what your business is going to be. Which is important to choosing the best domain name because your domain name should relate to your business and your brand. </p>\n<p>Start with a domain name generator tool to help you come up with some ideas. Try out the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-generator/\">IsItWP Free Domain Name Generator</a>. Just enter in 1 or 2 keywords for your business or blog. For instance, if you want to start a website for an accounting business, try typing in the keyword &#8220;accounting&#8221;. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/isitwp-domain-generator1.jpg\" alt=\"isitwp-domain-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"329\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228481\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/isitwp-domain-generator1.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/isitwp-domain-generator1-300x133.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>After you enter in the keyword, press the Generate Names button. The generator will then provide you with numerous domain name ideas that include your keyword. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/isitwp-domain-generator2.jpg\" alt=\"domain-name-ideas-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"464\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228482\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/isitwp-domain-generator2.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/isitwp-domain-generator2-300x188.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>With a domain name generator like this one, you’ll be able to brainstorm a ton of great domain name ideas for your website.</p>\n<p>Don’t forget that if you already have a domain name idea in mind, that you’ll need to do research to make sure it’s not already taken by someone else. </p>\n<h3>2. Pick the Right Domain Extension</h3>\n<p>When choosing a domain name for your blog or website, you also need to pick the right domain extension. A domain extension, which is also known as a Top Level Domain or TLD, is simply the suffix or the last part of a domain name. For example, with the domain name www.Google.com, .com is the domain extension. There are a number of different domain extensions that are used today, the most common ones include: </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>.com (commercial)</strong> &#8211; This is the most popular domain extension on the internet. It was originally created for commercial businesses but now it can be used for anything.</li>\n<li><strong>.biz (business)</strong> &#8211; This domain extension was created primarily for businesses whose preferred domain names were already taken with .com.</li>\n<li><strong>.org (organization)</strong> &#8211; Originally created for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-non-profits-charity-websites/\">non-profit organizations and charity websites</a> but now this domain name can be used by anyone.</li>\n<li><strong>.net (network)</strong> &#8211; An alternative to the popular .com domain extension that anyone can use, but originally created for network infrastructure use.</li>\n<li><strong>.edu (education)</strong> &#8211; This domain extension can only be used by accredited higher learning institutions like universities for instance.</li>\n<li><strong>.gov (government)</strong> &#8211; This domain extension can only be used by government entities.</li>\n<li><strong>Country specific</strong> &#8211; There are also domain extensions for specific countries like .ca for Canada and .in for India.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We recommend that you stick with .com for your domain extension because it’s the most credible and established domain extension. Plus, since .com is so synonymous with the internet, many users type in .com by default because they’re so used to it. For instance, if your domain name is AccountingByJudy.net, many users will instead type the more memorable domain extension .com without even thinking about it and won’t be able to find your website. This is especially common for users who aren’t tech-savvy. </p>\n<p>You want your website to be as easy to find as possible and to also appear credible, which is why we recommend choosing the .com domain extension. </p>\n<h3>3. Use Keywords</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/keywords.png\" alt=\"keywords\" width=\"740\" height=\"494\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231369\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/keywords.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/keywords-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/keyword-research-101-how-to-choose-the-right-terms-for-google/\" target=\"_blank\">Using keywords</a> is an important part in picking the best domain name. Keywords are how search engines can tell what your website is about. When someone searches for your keyword on the internet, if you include the keyword in your domain name, your website has a better chance of showing up near the top of search results. </p>\n<p>For example, if a user searches for photography services on Google, and your domain name is PreciousPhotography.com, your website is more likely to show up in their search results. Whereas if you don’t include keywords in your domain name and choose instead something like PreciousSnaps.com, your website may not show up in any search results for photography. It can be difficult to find a domain name that’s available for top keywords like “photography” but you just have to be creative and mix the keyword with other unique words to find the perfect combination. </p>\n<h3>4. Target Local Keywords</h3>\n<p>Regarding keywords, if you have a local business that’s focusing on a particular geographic area, you should target local keywords in your domain name as well. When users are searching for a business or service in their area, they typically add their city or state to the search to get results that are near them. For example, “landscaping Phoenix”. </p>\n<p>So, if you want to show up in local search results, add a local keyword to your domain name. Instead of BobsLandscaping.com, use BobsLandscapingPhoenix.com so that your website will show up in local search results. </p>\n<h3>5. Make it Easy to Type and Understand</h3>\n<p>When choosing a domain name, you might be tempted to come up a totally unique spelling to make your domain name stand out or change the spelling of a word because someone else took your preferred domain name. But, you should avoid picking a domain name that is too difficult for users to understand and type. </p>\n<p>If you change the spelling of a word in your domain name, for example, taking a domain name like ProfessionalPainting.com and turning it into ProfssnlPaintng.com, it will be more difficult for users to find your website. Try to avoid double letters as well. For example, a domain name like Glassstatues.com is likely to be typed incorrectly by users. Keep it simple and easy to type. </p>\n<h3>6. Keep it Short</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/easy-to-remember-domain-name.png\" alt=\"easy to remember domain name\" width=\"740\" height=\"494\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231368\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/easy-to-remember-domain-name.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/easy-to-remember-domain-name-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Nobody wants to type in a domain name that’s 64 characters long. Not only is it annoying for users, but it also increases the chances of misspellings that result in your website not being found and a loss of traffic. </p>\n<p>It’s much better to have a domain name that’s short and easy to remember. We recommend you keep your domain name under 15 characters long. </p>\n<h3>7. Avoid Numbers and Hyphens</h3>\n<p>You should avoid using numbers and hyphens in your domain name too. Numbers are often confusing for people because if you tell them “5” they might take it as “five”, which can lead to misspellings of your domain name. If you do need a number in your domain name because it’s in your business name for instance, you can register both variations to avoid this problem. </p>\n<p>You’ll want to avoid hyphens altogether as well because hyphens are often associated with spam domains and you don’t want people to think <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\">your website isn&#8217;t safe</a>. Hyphens also lead to misspellings because many users will forget to add a hyphen when typing your domain. </p>\n<h3>8. Don&#8217;t Be Generic &#8211; Be Unique</h3>\n<p>There are millions of registered domain names, so you have to make sure your domain name is unique and memorable. A domain name isn’t just your online address, it’s also part of your brand. So, while being easy to understand is important, it also has to be appealing and it has to represent who you are.  </p>\n<p>For example insurance.com is generic and boring, and it’s also probably already taken by someone. But a domain name like GuardedInsurance.com is unique and memorable, and it says to your potential customers that you’re a trustworthy company. Make sure your domain name will stand out in the minds of your website visitors.</p>\n<h3>9. Don&#8217;t Pigeonhole Yourself</h3>\n<p>When coming up with a unique domain name, it’s important not to pigeonhole yourself either. Picking a domain name that puts you in a box and only allows your business to be associated with one specific thing will present problems for you in the future when you want to grow and expand your business. </p>\n<p>Picture this: You start a business making handmade ceramic ornaments and choose your domain name to be CeramicOrnaments.com. In the future however, you want to start making other things like mugs, plates, bowls, etc. Consumers who are interested in those kitchenware items might pass over or never even discover your website because of its limited domain name. Pick a domain name that will give you room to grow. </p>\n<h3>Bonus Tip: Register your Domain Name for Free</h3>\n<p>Once you’ve picked the best domain name, you need to register your domain name in order to protect it from being taken by someone else. Plus, you’ll need to register your domain name in order to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">start building a website</a>. </p>\n<p>How do you register a domain name? Many website hosting companies offer a domain registration along with hosting. We recommend choosing <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Bluehost</a>, because you can get a FREE domain name, which is great if you’re just starting out. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png\" alt=\"bluehost-register-domain-name-free\" width=\"740\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228494\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Along with a free domain name, Bluehost is offering our readers an awesome deal on website hosting. If you’ve got the perfect domain name in mind, you can get a free domain name, free SSL, and over 60% off on WordPress hosting. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Sign up for Bluehost today so you can claim your preferred domain name and get started on making a successful website. </p>\n<p>We hope these tips helped you learn how to pick the best domain name. If you enjoyed this post and want to learn more about domain names and websites, check out another of our posts on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\">What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/pick-best-domain-name/\">How to Pick the Best Domain Name (&#038; How to Get It for Free)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://www.isitwp.com/pick-best-domain-name/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"11 Squarespace Alternatives for Every Kind of Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-alternatives-to-squarespace/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-alternatives-to-squarespace/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0: